<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="7" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1773,1919]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,1773,1799]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Remarks:</emphasis>
As explained in the introduction, regarding the general status of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Koenike" authorityYear="1910" box="[1098,1270,1773,1799]" class="Arachnida" family="Anisitsiellidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Anisitsiellidae</taxonomicName>
, I am not following 
<bibRefCitation author="Panesar, A. R." box="[239,416,1813,1839]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" pagination="1 - 144" refId="ref56187" refString="Panesar, A. R. (2004) Evolution in water mites (Hydrachnellae, Actinedida, Acari). A revision of the Anisitsiellidae Koenike, 1910. Bonner Zoologische Monographien, 52, 1 - 144." type="journal article" year="2004">Panesar (2004)</bibRefCitation>
but keep with the classification of the family according to 
<bibRefCitation author="Cook, D. R." box="[1105,1254,1813,1839]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" pagination="1 - 860" refId="ref55290" refString="Cook, D. R. (1974) Water mite genera and subgenera. Memoirs of the American Entomological Institute, 21, I - VII, 1 - 860." type="journal article" year="1974">Cook (1974)</bibRefCitation>
and K.O. 
<bibRefCitation author="Viets, K. O." pageId="6" pageNumber="7" refId="ref56590" refString="Viets, K. O. (1987) Die Milben des Susswassers (Hydrachnellae und Halacaridae [part.], Acari). 2: Katalog. Sonderbande des Naturwissenschaftlichen Vereins in Hamburg, 8, 1012 pp." type="book" year="1987">Viets (1987)</bibRefCitation>
. However, the generic and subgeneric classification (unless stated otherwise) follows the revision of 
<bibRefCitation author="Panesar, A. R." box="[151,331,1893,1919]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" pagination="1 - 144" refId="ref56187" refString="Panesar, A. R. (2004) Evolution in water mites (Hydrachnellae, Actinedida, Acari). A revision of the Anisitsiellidae Koenike, 1910. Bonner Zoologische Monographien, 52, 1 - 144." type="journal article" year="2004">Panesar (2004)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
